  <h1>The Ho System</h1>

  <p class="lede">Anyone can make an AI generate code. The gap is between
  “AI generated this” and “I built this”—and the bottleneck is judgment, not access.</p>

  <p class="claim">Structure the collaboration so the human keeps architectural authority and
  genuine understanding—and encode that structure in artifacts the AI conforms to. A
  <button type="button" class="term" data-term="ho" aria-expanded="false">ho</button> is one
  bounded, verified, recorded step; a sequence of them is a whole project.</p>

  <p><a class="cta" href="/walk/">{% koma 20, {"mode":"keyline","face":"front"} %} Take the walk →</a></p>
